c: 18
v: 57
t: "None ni nde muhemu mukuru gusumba uwibukiijwe amajambo y’Umuremyi wiwe nawe akaba atavyinezweho nukwibagira ivyabayeho kandi vyagizwe n’amaboko yiwe, twebwe twashize mumitima yabo imipfundikizo kugira ngo ntibatahure icarico cose no mumatwi yabo twashizeyo uburemere bw’ukutumva, rero ubahamagaye kubijanye n’uburokoke ntibemera kurokoka"